      renderContent: () => (
        <div className="space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p className="text-base">Fintech is unforgiving. A 5-minute outage can cost millions in lost transactions. A compliance error can trigger regulatory fines. A security breach can destroy trust overnight.</p>

          <p className="text-base">This is why operational excellence isn't optional in fintech—it's existential.</p>

          <h3 className="text-2xl font-semibold pt-4">The Three Dimensions of Fintech Excellence</h3>

          <div className="mt-6">
            <h4 className="font-bold text-lg mb-6">1. User Experience Simplicity</h4>
            <p className="mb-6 text-base">Cryptocurrency has 10,000+ coins. Picking the right ones requires expertise most users don't have. Our solution: theme-based baskets (Metaverse, DeFi, NFT, Web 3.0).</p>
            <p className="text-base">This wasn't just a feature—it was a philosophy. We reduced decision complexity from 10,000 options to 4. Onboarding time dropped by 50%.</p>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-8">
            <h4 className="font-bold text-lg mb-6">2. Operational Resilience</h4>
            <p className="mb-6 text-base">We built a 24/7 monitoring system with sub-5-minute issue resolution SLA. Every alert triggered an automated response:</p>
            <ul className="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li className="text-base">Wallet balance mismatches → Automatic reconciliation</li>
              <li className="text-base">API latency spikes → Automatic failover to backup systems</li>
              <li className="text-base">Unusual transaction patterns → Automatic fraud detection</li>
            </ul>
            <p className="text-base">Result: 99.2% uptime. Zero security breaches. Zero regulatory violations.</p>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-8">
            <h4 className="font-bold text-lg mb-6">3. Regulatory Compliance Automation</h4>
            <p className="mb-6 text-base">KYC/AML compliance is tedious and error-prone when done manually. We automated the entire workflow:</p>
            <ul className="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li className="text-base">Identity verification with 99.2% accuracy</li>
              <li className="text-base">Sanctions screening in real-time</li>
              <li className="text-base">Transaction monitoring with machine learning</li>
            </ul>
            <p className="text-base">Result: Compliance became a competitive advantage, not a cost center.</p>
          </div>

          <h3 className="text-2xl font-semibold pt-4">Key Takeaways</h3>
          <ul className="space-y-4 mt-6">
            <li className="flex gap-3">
