          <p className="text-base">Compliance is boring. It's expensive. It slows down product development. And it's absolutely essential.</p>

          <p className="text-base">Most fintech companies view compliance as a cost. We viewed it as a competitive advantage.</p>

          <div className="mt-6">
            <h4 className="font-bold text-lg mb-6">1. Trust with Users</h4>
            <p className="mb-6 text-base">When users see that you're compliant with SEC, FINRA, and GDPR, they trust you more. They're willing to deposit more money. They're less likely to churn.</p>
